Good thread from a pregnant black doctor who got the Pfizer COVID-19 vaccine.
I agree with her. There are few risks from the mRNA COVID vaccines and none that aren't greater in the flu shot, and the flu shot is tested and strongly recommended in pregnancy.
Thank you @tajayiMD https://t.co/tbVctsDrYt
